### We're just starting
Wait for an update, check out [inoio.de](http://inoio.de) or ping us [via email](mailto:hello@inoio.de).

### We're hiring
We're looking for great developers (mostly web, much java, some rails) that want to help us growing in Hamburg, Germany. You can also check out our [placement at XING](https://www.xing.com/jobs/hamburg-top-coder-java-web-festanstellung-gesucht-2165417) or just have a look at our [website](http://inoio.de).
